---
title: Thai Beef Salad with Carrot and Cucumber Ribbons, served over Jasmine Rice
description: This zippy steak salad is sure to be a weeknight dinner sensation. We love Thai food because it hits all the right flavour pillars - sweet, sour, salty and spicy!
